Don Haggerty https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_Haggerty 0 Don Haggerty (July 3, 1914 – August 19, 1988) was an American actor of film and television. Before he began appearing in films in 1947, Haggerty was a Brown University athlete and served in the United States military.
